                Tiberio Plautio Aeliano <lb n="2"/>Tauro Statilio Corvino co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>XIII <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iulia</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulus</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Ca</supplied>strici<supplied reason="lost">us Onesimus</supplied> <lb n="5"/>scripsi me promisisse <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Sulpicio Fausto quanta <lb n="7"/>pecunia ex auctione <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Servili Narcissi in stip<lb break="no" n="9"/>ulatum meum meo<lb break="no" n="10"/>rumque veniet vene<lb break="no" n="11"/>rit diducta <expan><abbr>mercede</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> in <lb n="12"/>representatum in HS <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>decem milia nummum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Es handelt sich um eine einzelne Tafel (Tabula Pompeiana 27). (B): Abweichende Lesungen. (C): Datum: AE 1973, Sbordone: 20.6.45; AE 1984: 20.5.45. Taurus nach Salomies bei Person 2 praenomen.</p>
            </div>
